<div class="jumbotron">
      <h1> <i class="icon-cogs"></i>&nbsp;&nbsp;<em>How NameCoach Works</em> </h1>
  </div>
             <% flash.each do |key, value| %>
              <div class="alert alert-block alert-<%=key%>"> 
              <button type="button" class="close" data-dismiss="alert">Ã—</button>
              <%= value %> 
              </div>
            <% end %>

<br/>
<br/>

<div class="container">

<div class="row">
    <div class="span10 offset1">
      <h3><em>NameCoach</em> customers purchase Event Pages, either by-the-event or through a monthly subscription.  An Event Page helps the MC for that event - say, a wedding, bar-mitzvah, or corporate function - to quickly and easily learn to perfectly pronounce every name.  Especially the tough ones. </h3>
    </div>
</div>

<br/>

<div class="row">
    <div class="span5 offset1">
      <h3>Here's how it works... </h3>
    </div>
</div>

<hr/><hr/>

<div class="row">
  <br/>
    <div class="span5">
      <h3><i class="icon-edit"></i>&nbsp;Create an Event Page </h3>
      <p><i class="icon-caret-right"></i>&nbsp;&nbsp;<span class="grabber2">Just enter a name (like 'The Jones-Ravenwood Wedding'), and a date for the event.</span></p>
    </div>
    <div class="span6">
     <%=  image_tag("create_event_4.png", alt: "Create Event", :class => "img-border") %>
     <h6> screenshots are scaled down </h6>
    </div>
  <br/>
</div>

<hr/><hr/>

<div class="row">
  <br/>
    <div class="span5">
      <h3><i class="icon-envelope"></i>&nbsp;Invite Other Admins&nbsp;<span class="muted">(optional)</span></h3>
      <p><i class="icon-caret-right"></i>&nbsp;&nbsp;<span class="grabber2">Once you create an Event Page, you will have 'admin' access to that page. Admins can request name recordings from attendees, listen to those recordings, and invite others to become admins (useful if the person requesting names and the person announcing them are different).</span></p>

      <p><i class="icon-caret-right"></i>&nbsp;&nbsp;<span class="grabber2">To invite an admin, you have two options:</spam></p>
        <ol>
          <li><span class="grabber2">Just enter an email address to send an admin invitation.  By clicking a link in this email, they will automatically become an admin for the event.</span></li> <br/>
          <li><span class="grabber2">Or, they can visit name-coach.com and sign up with the admin code.</span></li>
        </ol>
    </div>
    <div class="span6">
     <%=  image_tag("invite_admin_3.png", alt: "admin", :class => "img-border") %>
     </div>
     <div class="span4 offset1">
      <hr/>
     <%=  image_tag("admin_code_2.png", alt: "admin", :class => "img-border") %>
     <br/>
     <h6> screenshots are scaled down </h6>
    </div>
  <br/>
</div>

<hr/><hr/>

<div class="row">
  <br/>
    <div class="span5">
      <h3><i class="icon-envelope"></i>&nbsp;Invite Attendees to Record Names for that Event</h3>
      <p><i class="icon-caret-right"></i>&nbsp;&nbsp;<span class="grabber2">Admins have two options for inviting attendees:</span></p>
        <ol>
          <li><span class="grabber2">Just enter an email address to send an invitation via email.  By clicking a link in the invitation, they can immediately record their name for your event.</span></li> <br/>
          <li><span class="grabber2">Or, give them a unique link generated for your event. Just copy and paste the link into a web page or mass email.</span></li>
        </ol>
    </div>
    <div class="span6">
      <%= image_tag("invite_attendee_3.png", alt: "invite", :class => "img-border") %>
     </div>
     <div class="span4 offset1">
      <hr/>
     <%=  image_tag("event_link_wc_2.png", alt: "event code", :class => "img-border") %>
     <br/>
     <h6> screenshots are scaled down </h6>
    </div>
  <br/>
</div>

<hr/><hr/>

<div class="row">
  <br/>
    <div class="span5">
      <h3><i class="icon-volume-up"></i>&nbsp;Attendees Record their Names</h3>
      <p><i class="icon-caret-right"></i>&nbsp;&nbsp;<span class="grabber2">Whichever method you use, attendees click a link to record their names using our online voice-recorder.  They can also enter exactly how they want to be announced (middle names, titles), and notes to help with pronounciation ('last name rhymes with.. ').</span></p>
    </div>
    <div class="span5 offset1">
      <%= image_tag("record_2_2.png", alt: "invite", :class => "img-border") %>
      <h6> screenshots are scaled down </h6>
    </div>
  <br/>
</div>

<hr/><hr/>

<div class="row">
  <br/>
    <div class="span5">
      <h3><i class="icon-play-circle"></i>&nbsp;Hear and Practice those Names</h3>
      <p><i class="icon-caret-right"></i>&nbsp;&nbsp;<span class="grabber2">After an attendee records their name, MC's/admins can hear those names on the Event Page and see any attendees' pronunciation notes. They can also enter their own helpful notes.</span></p>   
    </div>
    <div class="span5 offset1">
      <%= image_tag("event_page_22.png", alt: "event_page", :class => "img-border") %>
      <h6> screenshots are scaled down </h6>
    </div>
  <br/>
</div>

<hr/><hr/>

<div class="row">
  <div class="span4 offset1">
    <p><a class="btn btn-primary btn-large bg-purple" href="<%= value_path %>">See Why People Love NameCoach! <i class="icon-chevron-right icon-white"></i> </a></p>
  </div>
  <div class="span4 offset3">
    <p><a class="btn btn-primary btn-large bg-purple" href="<%= pricing_path %>">Start Your Free Trial! <i class="icon-chevron-right icon-white"></i> </a></p>
  </div>
</div>

<hr/>

</div>
